-- Russian Opposition Plans Rally for Sept. 15, Kommersant Reports
-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 2012-08-31T04:37:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-31/russian-opposition-plans-rally-for-sept-15-kommersant-reports.html
Russia’s opposition is seeking the
authorities’ approval to hold a rally of as many as 50,000
people on Sept. 15, Kommersant reported, citing activist Sergei
Udaltsov.  To contact the reporter on this story:
